Package entities

Class Passenger

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Thread
      • entities.Passenger
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Runnable
    public class Passenger
extends java.lang.Thread
    This datatype implements the Passenger thread. In his lifecycle, the passenger arrives at the airport, and decides on his course of action:
    • Retrieves his bags, if he has any, then goes home;
    • Goes to the departure terminal if he's not at his final destination;
    • Or if he has no bags and is in his final destination, immediatly goes home.
